<BlogLayout title="Scrabble Words With K — The 5-Point Singleton" description="Master K words in Scrabble: KAYAK (16pts), KNACK (15pts), QUIRKY (22pts). Only 1 K tile in the bag — learn how to manage and maximize this rare 5-point letter." keywords="scrabble words with k, k words scrabble, kayak scrabble, knack scrabble, quirky scrabble, k tile strategy, high scoring k words">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Article","headline":"Scrabble Words With K — The 5-Point Singleton","description":"Master K words in Scrabble with scoring breakdowns and management strategy for the only K tile in the bag.","datePublished":"2026-06-30","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"ScrabbleWordsFinder.com","url":"https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com"},"publisher":{"@type":"Organization","name":"ScrabbleWordsFinder.com"},"mainEntityOfPage":{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/scrabble-words-with-k"}})} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How many K tiles are in Scrabble?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"There is only 1 K tile in a standard Scrabble game, worth 5 points. This makes K the rarest mid-value tile and one you must deploy strategically when you draw it."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What is the highest-scoring K word in Scrabble?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"QUIRKY scores 22 points without premium squares, combining Q (10pts) with K (5pts) and Y (4pts). It's one of the few words that uses both Q and K together."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Should you save K for premium squares?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes — K on a DLS gives 10 points from one tile, and on TLS gives 15. If a premium square is accessible within 1-2 turns, hold K rather than playing it on a regular square for just 5 points."}}]})} />
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12"><article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
    <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1"><a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a><span class="mx-1">›</span><span class="text-gray-300">Strategy</span></nav>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Scrabble Words With K — The 5-Point Singleton</h1>
    <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400"><time datetime="2026-06-30">June 30, 2026</time><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><span>5 min read</span><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a></div>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">K is worth 5 points with only 1 tile in the entire bag — making it the rarest mid-value letter. When you draw K, you've got a tile that demands respect: enough points to be valuable on premium squares, but awkward enough in English that it can clog your rack if you don't know the right words.</p>
